 &lt;p&gt;⭐️&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;題目連結&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#題目連結&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 題目連結&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly96ZXJvanVkZ2UudHcvU2hvd1Byb2JsZW0/cHJvYmxlbWlkPWQwOTc=&#34;&gt;ZeroJudge&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9vbmxpbmVqdWRnZS5vcmcvZXh0ZXJuYWwvMTAwL3AxMDAzOC5wZGY=&#34;&gt;題目連結&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9vbmxpbmVqdWRnZS5vcmcvaW5kZXgucGhwP29wdGlvbj1jb21fb25saW5lanVkZ2UmYW1wO0l0ZW1pZD04JmFtcDtjYXRlZ29yeT0xMiZhbXA7cGFnZT1zaG93X3Byb2JsZW0mYW1wO3Byb2JsZW09OTc5&#34;&gt;Online Judge&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudWRlYnVnLmNvbS9VVmEvMTAwMzg=&#34;&gt;uDebug&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;題目說明&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#題目說明&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 題目說明&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Time limit: 3.000 seconds&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;題目&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#題目&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 題目&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A sequence of  &lt;code&gt;n &amp;gt; 0&lt;/code&gt;  integers is called a jolly jumper if the absolute values of the difference between successive elements take on all the values  &lt;code&gt;1&lt;/code&gt;  through  &lt;code&gt;n − 1&lt;/code&gt; . For instance,&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1 4 2 3&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;is a jolly jumper, because the absolutes differences are  &lt;code&gt;3&lt;/code&gt; ,  &lt;code&gt;2&lt;/code&gt; , and  &lt;code&gt;1&lt;/code&gt;  respectively. The definition implies that any sequence of a single integer is a jolly jumper. You are to write a program to determine whether or not each of a number of sequences is a jolly jumper.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;input&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#input&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Input&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Each line of input contains an integer  &lt;code&gt;n ≤ 3000&lt;/code&gt;  followed by  &lt;code&gt;n&lt;/code&gt;  integers representing the sequence.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;output&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#output&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Output&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For each line of input, generate a line of output saying  &lt;code&gt;‘Jolly’&lt;/code&gt;  or  &lt;code&gt;‘Not jolly’&lt;/code&gt; .&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;details class=&#34;success&#34;&gt;&lt;summary&gt;單字&lt;/summary&gt;&lt;div&gt;
